Our Products


Coal Sales

								We are ready to serve you with over 13 percent 
								of America's annual coal supply.  We mine 
								and sell predominantly cleaner-burning, 
								low-sulfur steam, metallurgical and PCI coals. 
								

								The coal quality (average Btu and SO2 content) 
								from each of our mines is estimated within the “Our 
								Mines” section and in our products guide.

								We operate 10 modern and large-scale mining 
								complexes in the 
								eastern and western United States that have 
								access to every major rail system as well as 
								competitive access to inland waterways and 
								export facilities from the East, West and Gulf 
								coasts. 

								Whether you need spot pricing or a long-term 
								contract, you can count on Arch Coal. Contact us 
								today.


