Careers
				
Career Search









Careers

                                If your career is built around hard work and 
								dedication, and if you're seeking a company with 
								a culture based on opportunity and autonomy - 
								we'd like to invite you to explore career 
								opportunities with Arch Coal.

								At Arch Coal, you would be a part of one of the 
								largest coal producers in the U.S. We have 
								employees in eight states, including our 
								corporate headquarters in St. Louis. We employ 
								approximately 4,000 hardworking individuals 
								across the U.S. in a variety of jobs from 
								accountants to machine operators to 
								environmental engineers.

We strive to be the employer of choice, from our great 
				benefits package to our focus on training for career 
				enhancement.

								Because our success 
								depends on the determination and dedication of 
								our employees, we recognize our employees as 
								highly valued resources. In addition to an 
								environment conducive to personal and 
								professional growth, we offer excellent 
								compensation packages and outstanding benefits, 
								such as medical, prescription drug, dental, 
								vision, life and disability insurance, 
								retirement savings, and educational assistance.
								 

Begin your 
									career search






